glosses: To lower something solid into something liquid or acts like a liquid; to dip, to dunk.

etymology: From Ottoman Turkish بانمق (banmak, “to dip into a fluid”), from Proto-Turkic *ban- (“to dip”). Cognate to Karakhanid [script needed] (manmāq, “to dip”), Chagatai [script needed] (manmaq, “to dip”).
